data.description:
Welcome to this stunning property in the heart of peace and tranquility.  The open kitchen allows for great entertaining opening into a massive living and dining room space.  A newly renovated master bedroom suite with new hardwood engineered floors and a new master bedroom with no detail left undone.   The home includes a utility room with a washer and dryer, mudroom and a gorgeous pantry area.  This home has had almost every space updated and transformed.  There are 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms just on the first floor.  A large sunlit living room, a wood burning fireplace, a multitude of windows that boast a gorgeous pond and breathtaking views.  You have the rare opportunity if you choose to own your dream home and have a portion of it financed with a fully functional AIR BNB in the finished full basement (the basement square footage is in addition to the 2800 sq ft noted on the first floor)  bringing in on average and above $1200-1400 of income per month. There is also an outdoor entertaining space.

Please note~ Property will include 5 newly surveyed acres with the homestead.  New survey info will be pending.
